OL,3,CDo the Palestinians have their own
OL,4,CMandela-like figure in waiting?
OL,6,FA new documentary asks if Marwan
OL,7,FBarghouti could help find a way to
OL,8,Fpeace after the war in Gaza, ITV News
OL,9,FCorrespondent Rachel Younger reports
OL,11,FAmong all of the headlines coming out
OL,12,Fof the Middle East since the war
OL,13,Fbegan, one name rarely mentioned is
OL,14,FMarwan Barghouti.
OL,16,FBut he is at the heart of the
OL,17,Fdeadlocked ceasefire negotiations
OL,18,Fbetween the two sides.
