OL,3,CDo the Palestinians have their own
OL,4,CMandela-like figure in waiting?
OL,6,FNot because he has taken part in them
OL,7,F- Barghouti has been inside Israeli
OL,8,Fprisons for 22 years - but because he
OL,9,Fis someone Hamas insist must be freed
OL,10,Fif there's to be another exchange of
OL,11,FIsraeli hostages.
OL,13,FMany Israelis see Barghouti as an arch-
OL,14,Fterrorist, but Tomorrow's Freedom, a
OL,15,Fdocumentary released this week, asks
OL,16,Fif he could help find a way to peace
OL,17,Fafter the war.
OL,19,FThe film was made before the conflict
OL,20,Fbegan.
