OL,3,CDo the Palestinians have their own
OL,4,CMandela-like figure in waiting?
OL,6,FAs its director Sophia Scott
OL,7,Facknowledges, it is not an easy
OL,8,Fquestion to pose with Israel still
OL,9,Freeling from and Gaza devastated by
OL,10,Fthe scale of .
OL,12,F"One of the only good things that has
OL,13,Fcome about is that people are asking
OL,14,Fwhat about the day after. It's hard
OL,15,Fwhen people are being killed, but what
OL,16,Fhappens the day after when peace
OL,17,Fhopefully ?," Ms Scott said.
