OL,3,CDo the Palestinians have their own
OL,4,CMandela-like figure in waiting?
OL,6,F"Who can create that? Now Barghouti is
OL,7,Fsomeone not only Palestinians but also
OL,8,FIsraelis and international politicians
OL,9,Frecognise could bridge that massive
OL,10,Fgap between Israelis and Palestinians
OL,11,Fand among Palestinians as well. But
OL,12,Fhe's languishing in jail."
OL,14,FTomorrow's Freedom is an intimate
OL,15,Fportrait of Barghouti's wife and
OL,16,Fchildren, as they struggle to get any
OL,17,Faccess to him.
