OL,3,CDo the Palestinians have their own
OL,4,CMandela-like figure in waiting?
OL,6,FThe film charts his path, as an
OL,7,Felected Fatah member of parliament, as
OL,8,Fone of the strongest backers of the
OL,9,FOslo Peace Accords in the 1990s, to
OL,10,Fdisillusionment as the international
OL,11,Fcommunity failed to end the Israeli
OL,12,Foccupation.
OL,14,FIt gives voice to some of those who've
OL,15,Fcampaigned for his freedom like the
OL,16,Fformer US President Jimmy Carter and
OL,17,FArchbishop Desmond Tutu.
