OL,4,CMandela-like figure in waiting?
OL,6,FBut while polls still show that he is
OL,7,Fthe leader most Palestinians want, his
OL,8,Fson Arab, who lives in the West Bank,
OL,9,Ftold ITV News he just wants his father
OL,10,Fback home.
OL,12,FWith at least 13 in Israeli prisons
OL,13,Fsince October 7, his fear is palpable.
OL,15,F"For my father's case they want to set
OL,16,Fan example," Arab said. "He was put in
OL,17,Fa very tiny cell, given minimal food,
OL,18,Fhe's already lost 10 kilograms.
