OL,6,F"For weeks they put speakers on at
OL,7,Fhigh volume so he couldn't sleep and
OL,8,Fshone a spotlight in his face. They
OL,9,Ftake his mattress, the only thing in
OL,10,Fhis cell, from 5am to 9pm.
OL,12,F"On March 9 a few of the prison guards
OL,13,Fbeat him until he passed out and then
OL,14,Fleft him for three hours. When he woke
OL,15,Fup he was full of blood. He didn't get
OL,16,Fmedical treatment."
