OL,6,FFearful though he is, Arab says he
OL,7,Ffeels guilty complaining about what
OL,8,Fhis family is going through "when (he
OL,9,Fsees) 2.3 million people in Gaza
OL,10,Flosing everything, their homes, ".
OL,12,F"All he is thinking about is the
OL,13,Fsuffering of the Palestinian people
OL,14,Fand how he can bring that suffering to
OL,15,Fan end," Arab said.
OL,17,FWhen asked how he can defend a man
OL,18,FIsrael judges a terrorist he sighs
OL,19,Fdeeply.
