OL,6,F"It fascinates me that everyone knows
OL,7,Fthat Israel's occupation is illegal.
OL,8,FThat Benjamin Netanyahu is breaking
OL,9,Finternational law by targeting
OL,10,Fchildren in Gaza.
OL,12,F"My father hasn't just been working
OL,13,Ffor peace for a few years. He was a
OL,14,Fbig supporter of the two-state
OL,15,Fsolution and the Oslo Accords even
OL,16,Fwhen many Palestinians disapproved of
OL,17,Fthat. That is the kind of leader he
OL,18,Fis."
