OL,6,F"I think it very much depends on what
OL,7,Fhe says and does when he comes out,
OL,8,Fassuming he is released," she said.
OL,9,F"Whether he continues to advocate
OL,10,Fviolence or whether he draws a line
OL,11,Funder violence and moves to diplomacy.
OL,13,F"To say: 'Okay, now is the time to
OL,14,Fensure that the occupation ends,
OL,15,FPalestinians get their state. The
OL,16,Fwhole world is of that opinion, Israel
OL,17,Fis trailing somewhat behind, still
OL,18,Fsuffering from the trauma of October
OL,19,F7. Let's engage with the Israelis
OL,20,Fconstructively to ensure that they
OL,21,Ffeel secure'.
