OL,3,CDo the Palestinians have their own
OL,4,CMandela-like figure in waiting?
OL,6,F"That is what it boils down to," she
OL,7,Fsaid.
OL,9,FBar-Yaacov stresses the role Barghouti
OL,10,Fmight play would depend on any
OL,11,Fconditions surrounding his release,
OL,12,Fthe will of the Palestinian people and
OL,13,Fwhether their existing government of
OL,14,FMahmoud Abbas and any future Israeli
OL,15,Fadministration would work with him.
OL,17,FThat's a lot of 'ifs'.
OL,19,FBut she recognises his record of being
OL,20,Fable to bring different factions
OL,21,Ftogether.
